						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājēndra I. Year lost. (A.D. 1012-1044).</hi></p>						

						<p>Unfinished and built in at the top and left side. Seems to record a grant of land for providing sacred food to the deity in the temple of Agastīśvaram Uḍaiyār by the <hi rend="italic">mahāsabha</hi> of Nālūr, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Chēṟṟūr-kūṟṟam.</p>						

